34. Affiliate marketing: Promote products as an affiliate marketer through websites like Amazon Associates or Commission Junction.
35. Blogging: Monetize a blog through advertising, sponsored content, and affiliate marketing.
36. Stock trading: Buy and sell stocks through a brokerage firm or trading platform.
37. Online bookkeeping: Offer bookkeeping services to businesses or individuals through platforms like Upwork or Fiverr.
38. Virtual bookkeeping: Offer virtual bookkeeping services to businesses or individuals through platforms like Upwork or Fiverr.
39. Online tutoring: Offer online tutoring services through websites like Tutor.com or Chegg.
40. Online consulting: Offer online consulting services in your area of expertise through platforms like Clarity or Coach.me.
